<table  border=0 cellpadding=2 cellspacing=0 awidth=100%><a name=102156964720336></a><form action=http://eqdb.allakhazam.com/strategy/mrate.pl name=f102156964720336><tr><td id=headerrow><a id=sj href=classes.html?class=4&mid=102156964720336>RE: Little help</a> <a id=fs8 href=classes.html?class=4&mid=102156964720336#post><img src=http://everquest.allakhazam.com/static/reply.gif border=0 alt="Reply..." height=16 width=16></a></td><td align=right id=headerrow valign=bottom><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=61546><span id=Scholar>Slipskin</span></a>, <span id=Scholar>Scholar</span><br><span id=notbold>278 posts</td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 id=headerrow>Posted @ Thu, May 16th 1:29 PM 2002</td>
	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Good<span id=notbold>[3.65]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>Stick with East Commons for now. Black Bears make good targets.&nbsp;&nbsp;You could get lucky and pick up an HQ bear skin that you can sell for 30pp to other player/tailors.  Spiderlings are good. Sell stacks of silks to tailors.  You could hunt EC all the way to level 13 or so. Then go to West Commons and go after willowisps. Sell the Lightstones to vendors for 8-10gp each.  Keep the Greater Lightstones.  When you have all the Grt Lightstones you can carry use Selo's to run to North Karana.  One of the gypsy girls, Myrsella (?) will take the GLS's in trade and return you a Concordance of Research and some experience.  Sell the Concordance back to her for 8-9pp each.  When you get to level 16 start hunting North Karana. Kill more wisps, grizzly bears, and any beetles that con even or blue.  That will get you to 18.  At level 17 or 18 go to East Karana.  Kill snakes/chasm crawlers. Collect the poison sacs and sell them to passing Rogues.  Kill the doggies too, for experience.  That will take you into the low 20's.<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
